channel.description:
What you are doing: Making it so if a normal player obtains a donator only item, it will not let them equip it, and making a donator only zone

Difficulty -1302102343/1000000000
Knowledge needed: Basic Java
Files edited: Client.java, Shops.cfg, Autospawn.cfg, item.cfg (optional).


Step 1: Making your item Donator only

Open Client.java, and search up 

[code]public boolean wear(int wearID, int slot) {[/code]

You should see something like this...

[code]if(wearID == 5509){
emptySmallPouch();
return false;
}
if(wearID == 5510){
emptyMediumPouch();
return false;
}
if(wearID == 5512){
emptyLargePouch();
return false;
}
if(wearID == 5514){
emptyGiantPouch();
return false;
}
if(wearID == 6570 && killedJad == 0){
sM("You must have defeated TzTok-Jad to wear this cape.");
return false;
}
if(wearID == 7808 && playerRights != 3){
sM("How the fuck did you get this...owner+ item..");
return false;
}[/code]

Under the } add this...

[code]if(wearID == #### && donator == 0){
sM("You are not donator, so you cannot equip this.");
return false;
}[/code]

#### = Item id that you want to be donator only

What we just did: We made it that so if normal player gets a donator only item and try's to equip it, It won't let him and it will send him the message specifed there. (You are not donator, so you cannot equip this)

Step 1.1: Making the Donator Weapon have high hits! (Optional)

Open item.cfg and search for your donator item, the example im going to use is "anger sword" when you search your item you should see this but with your item..

[code]item = 7806	Anger_sword	A_heavy_duty_sword.	9999999	9999999	9999999	9999999	9999999	9999999	9999999	9999999	9999999	0	0	0	0	0	0[/code]

change all the numbers to what you want the stat bonuses to be using this format...

[code]1: Shop Price
2: Low Alch Value
3: High Alch Value
4: Stab Att Boost
5: Slash Att Boost
6: Crush Att Boost
7: Magic Att Boost
8: Range Att Boost
9: Stab Def Boost
10: Slash Def Boost
11: Crush Def Boost
12: Magic Def Boost
13: Range Def Boost
14: Strength Boost
15: Prayer Boost[/code]

Remember to keep the spaces tabbed or you will get an exception error.

What we just did: Changed the stat bonus for item.

Step 2: Making the command to tele to the donator zone.

Go into client.java and search up 

[code]if(command.startsWith("mypos")[/code]

You should see a bunch of commands, under the } put this

[code]if (command.equalsIgnoreCase("donatorzone") && donator >= 1) {
triggerTele(####, @@@@, 0);
sM("You teleport to the donator zone.");
}[/code]

#### = X coord
@@@@ = Y coord

What we just did: If a donator in you server did ::donatorzone he would be teled to the coords you put. and would be sent the message: "You teleport to the donator zone"

